                Caelesti Aeternae <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>aedem a solo cum pronao et co<lb break="no" n="3"/>lumnis et sedibus phosphoris <lb n="4"/>exstrucxit <note>sic</note> <expan><abbr>idemq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>dedic</abbr><ex>avit</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>item vicum qui subiacet huic <lb n="6"/>templo &amp;lt;l=I&amp;gt;oncum <note>sic</note> |(pedes<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> CCCL cum <lb n="7"/>aedifici&amp;lt;i=T&amp;gt;s omnibus et columnis <lb n="8"/>et porticibus et arcus IIII <lb n="9"/>idem fecit et nundinas insti<lb break="no" n="10"/>tuit qui vicus nomine ipsius <lb n="11"/>appellatur 
            </ab></div>
